Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.54,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know what I should do now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.71,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}With every strength I can take to break enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:48.40,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絶縁體のような表情で　抵抗を嫌う口実を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:52.65,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}共振拒む理由なんて　単純すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.71,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:10.25,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I won't let you down come along with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.01,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Taking back my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.97,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}確信はその手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:26.27,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm waiting for till the break of dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.77,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Taking back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:32.02,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}錆付いた意志でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.40,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.07,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}革命に似た Calling back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.28,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tell me what's wrong with the society
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.28,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}that everybody is saying OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:46.08,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Low resistance of high zest inner cells
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.12,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Rebuild the coil there is no lie
Comment: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.54,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我現在該做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.71,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}明明有了一切擊敗敵人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:48.40,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你露出絕緣體般的表情 說著不願抵抗的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:52.65,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但拒絕共振的理由 卻太過單純
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.71,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為何不嘗試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:10.25,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不會讓你失望 隨我前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.01,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要奪回我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.72,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}為何不嘗試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.97,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}信心就在你的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:26.27,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我會等待 直到黎明破曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.77,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}奪回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:32.02,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即便意志已然鏽蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.40,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是改變這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.07,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}革命一般 回收一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.28,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}這個社會究竟怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.28,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大家為何習以為常？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:46.08,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}高功率內細胞的低電阻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.12,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重建構線圈 讓一切謊言煙消雲散
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:47.79,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,灰色の街に一粒の雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:53.79,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,息を止めた記憶の囚われ人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:56.41,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,瞼に焼き付く烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.21,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,脆いナイフ振り回し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:03.17,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,崩れ落ちた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:09.25,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとスローに見える世界に閉じ込められ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:15.11,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつの間にか自分すら憎んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:20.22,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,禁断の果実に手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:27.47,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,名前のない細胞が叫ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:33.36,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,閃光よ　走り出せ　幻を暴くようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:38.70,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,完璧を求める「異常」な時代に Siren
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:43.93,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,胸の奥　鳴り響く　確かな疑惑の Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:49.07,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,諸刃の感情　自分を貫く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.97,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,「始まりと終わり」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:24:01.48,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,その境界線上で1つの可能性　切り開け
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:47.79,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,落入灰暗街道的一粒雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:53.79,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,深陷記憶牢籠的人不禁止住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:56.41,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,眼瞼上的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.21,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,揮動脆弱的匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:03.17,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,未來已是一片廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:09.25,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,悶在緩慢流逝的封閉世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:15.11,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺連自我都變得可憎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:20.22,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,向禁斷之果伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:27.47,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,無名的細胞吶喊道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:33.36,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,閃光啊 奔跑吧 讓一切虛幻現於光天化日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:38.70,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,為苛求完美的「異常」時代拉響警報
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:43.93,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷吶喊的心聲 訴說著無法調和的疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:49.07,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,雙刃的感情刺穿了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.97,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,「起始與終結」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:24:01.48,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,將兩者之間一絲的可能性 打開
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真淵京馬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京馬先生 別衝動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會來 格倫德爾的倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道你會來 敗犬
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
